{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessSignalName\/notify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"SubprocessSignalName.notify","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Case","externalID":"s:3GIO20SubprocessSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/subprocesssignalname\/notify"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SubprocessSignalName"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":